abstract: Europe leads United States in Walker Cup amateur biennial golf event at Royal Lytham and St Annes in England; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Jimmy Mullen won all four matches he played in the two-day amateur event as the Britain and Ireland team regained the Walker Cup with its highest points total.

headline.main: Britain and Ireland Team Tops U.S. at Walker Cup
